attributes.title: My breakfast
attributes.description:
Created on August 25, 2010 by leila on Sourcemap.org:

After making this map I started to think more about food that I buy and eat. As you will see food that I have in my kitchen comes from Slovenia, Bosnia, Croatia, Italy and Switzerland.
